data.actual_result: Only the one with 50 steps pops up; to load the other entries, you'll have to pull down as if you're trying to scroll.
data.short_description: If you have an entry with 50 steps at the top in Audit log and open the log, only the first entry (i.e. the one with 50 steps) loads.
data.steps_to_repro: - Make changes to a role 50 times (or do anything that gives you 50 steps in an entry). - Open Audit log.
